author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Exhaust fan electrical tips…push-in connectors protect wires and are required. Extending stranded wire 1/8” beyond the copper keeps it tight inside the wire nut. All this makes wiring safer inside any bathroom exhaust fan. Many thanks to Panasonic for providing the Whisper Cozy to my client on this project ❤️#exhaustfan #bathroomrenovation #diy #brandpartner
